summary: just finished luke cage season 2! pretty crazy stuff! i enjoyed the season and am looking forward to future episodes :D ive read...
body: just finished luke cage season 2! pretty crazy stuff! i enjoyed the season and am looking forward to future episodes :D ive read way more daredevil comics than luke cage comics tbh and matt tried something very simmilar to what luke is doing in his own neighborhood. wonder if being the king of harlem will work out as well for luke as i remember it working for matt in the comics (aka not very well) and if im remembering correctly, luke tried to talk matt out of taking over hells kitchen. its not really surprising that the characterization is somewhat different in the tv shows than the comics, i think we’ve already seen that to be true. guess we’ll have to see how it turns out!
